@startuml
title Observable Signature Gauge Entry Round

skinparam componentStyle rectangle

component "Arithmetic budget\nL0(state)" as L0
component "Delta to Q distortion\nweightedSupport + trackedSupport" as DQ
component "Signature stress\nforced / conditional / blocked / held" as Sig
component "Observable transport gate\nadmissible + stable + coherent" as Obs
component "Pressure test instance\ncanonical singleton" as Test
component "Shift pressure test\npointwise pressure status" as ShiftTest
component "Gauge entry\nfiber/action laws" as Gauge
component "Canonical execution receipt\nidentity step" as Exec
component "Live shift execution receipt\ntrajectory i0 -> i1" as ShiftExec
component "Physics receipt\nexecution + statuses + support budget" as Receipt

L0 --> DQ : finite budget
DQ --> Sig : controlled carrier path
Sig --> Test : signature forced
Obs --> Test : observable forced
Sig --> ShiftTest : promotion-ready endpoints
Obs --> ShiftTest : held/control separation
Test --> Gauge : minimal entry, no matter claim
Exec --> Receipt : admissible identity step
ShiftExec --> Receipt : admissible shift step
Test --> Receipt : promotion evidence
ShiftTest --> Receipt : shift-backed status evidence
DQ --> Receipt : pair support decomposition
Obs --> Receipt : observableStatus
Sig --> Receipt : signatureStatus

note bottom of Gauge
G is abstract.
No Standard Model or matter recovery claim.
end note

@enduml
